{
  "texts": [
    "Each chunk of the music file is mono-recorded with a 16 kHz sampling rate.",
    "It spans a broad range of genres, making it suitable for pretraining.",
    "First, ensure the each chunk has the same length of 30 s by using replication padding.",
    "Then, the transforms of the raw audio using various augmentation methods (\"Effective data augmentation\" section) to create the positive pairs.",
    "To convert the audio sequence into log-Mel spectrogram with the same setting of DCASE2019 Subtask 1C."
  ]
}